@@TJvArrangeSettings
Summary
  Helper class that specifies the properties of an autoarranging panel
Description
  TJvArrangeSettings is the class of the TJvPanel.AutoArrange property. It has properties for
  controling the behavior when auto arranging controls put on the panel.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvArrangeSettings.Assign
Summary
  Copies the values of another object to this object
Description
  Call Assign to copy the values of another TJvArrangeSettings to the current object. If Source is not
  a TJvArrangeSettings or descendant, the inherited Assign method is called
Parameters
  Source - The object to copy from. This object must be of type TJvArrangeSettings (or a descendant)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvArrangeSettings.AutoArrange
Summary
  Specifies whether auto arranging is active or not
Description
  Set AutoArrange to true to active auto arranging of child controls on a panel

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvArrangeSettings.AutoSize
Summary
  Determines what type of auto sizing is applied to the controls on a panel
Description
  Use AutoSize to specify how controls on the panel should be sized and moved when the panel is sized
  or controls are auto arranged on the panel

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvArrangeSettings.BorderLeft
